detaileddescription.para: Some functions from ZV_Lib_Diagnosis need Tresos configuration. The following requirements are covered by the Tresos configuration: SWR_ICAS1_GW_21228 SWR_ICAS1_GW_21229 SWR_ICAS1_GW_21231 SWR_ICAS1_GW_21194 SWR_ICAS1_GW_21232 SWR_ICAS1_GW_21230 SWR_ICAS1_GW_21193 The traceability between these requirements and module test is covered in Lib_Integration.c.test.
